================================================================================
PURPOSE
================================================================================

operator-commons is a shared Go library for Kubernetes operator scaffolding.
It provides reusable abstractions for:

- pkg/finalizer    — finalizer helpers (stdlib slices only)
- pkg/labels       — recommended K8s labels builder + v2 mapping
- pkg/status       — Condition Type catalog + helpers
- pkg/storageclass — DNS-1123 storageClass validator + Normalize
- pkg/version      — semver-aware version matrix helpers
- pkg/monitoring   — ServiceMonitor / PrometheusRule helpers (CRD-soft)
- pkg/networkpolicy— opinionated NetworkPolicy builders (deny-by-default)
- pkg/security     — restricted-PSA SecurityContext helpers
- pkg/events       — Kubernetes Event recorder + Reason catalog
- pkg/probes       — corev1.Probe fluent builder
- pkg/pvc          — PVC expansion helpers
- pkg/topology     — PVC topology spread helpers
- pkg/webhook      — admission validation helpers

This is a library — it does not distribute container images, binaries, or
operator manifests on its own.

